casebody.data:
No. 10-6548. LaVern Berryhill, Petitioner v. Edward Evans, et al. 562 U.S. 1057, 131 S. Ct. 649,

178 L. Ed. 2d 472,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9263. November 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
